name: Uashmama Paperbag silver
description:
You can use the Paper Bag to cover a vase, for laundry, for kids toys...
The bags are designed to be rolled so you can alter the height to suit the contents.

UASHMAMA paper bags (pronounced Wash Mama), paper bags that feel like leather, wash like fabric and flatten for easy storage.

UASHMAMA® paper is made using a virgn fibre through cultivation and NOT through deforestation. Paper that washes like fabric holding it's form so it can be used over and over again, promoting sustainabilty perfect for catering and homewares.

All UASHMAMA® bags are designed and made in Tuscany.

material: 100% cellulose
3 Sizes available

Washing instructions
Unroll bag and wash in warm water (30 degrees) with a mild soap, then rinse thoroughly and dry flat. Hand wash only, do not machine wash,do not dry clean.
